OL,3,CChild rapist jailed for 22 years
OL,5,FA child rapist from Chatham, Kent has
OL,6,Fbeen jailed for 22 years.
OL,8,FBilly Ward was sentenced at Maidstone
OL,9,FCrown Court on Friday (7 June) after a
OL,10,Fjury found him guilty of 12 charges
OL,11,Fwhich included rape of a child under
OL,12,F13 and assault of a child under 13 by
OL,13,Ftouching.
OL,15,FHe had denied the charges after being
OL,16,Farrested in October 2023. Ward, of
OL,17,FCastle Road, committed the offences
OL,18,Fagainst the young child between
OL,19,FJanuary 2016 and October 2022.
