OL,5,FDuring the sentencing, the 40-year-old
OL,6,Fwas handed a 22-year jail term and
OL,7,Fordered to serve an extended licence
OL,8,Fof five years. He was also handed a
OL,9,FSexual Harm Prevention Order which
OL,10,Fwill remain in place for 35 years.
OL,12,FInvestigating officer Detective
OL,13,FConstable Emma Othen of Kent Police's
OL,14,FVulnerability Investigation Team said:
OL,15,F'Ward carried out pre-planned and
OL,16,Fsustained offending over a six-year
OL,17,Fperiod against a vulnerable young
OL,18,Fchild.
