OL,5,F"His crimes are some of the worst I
OL,6,Fhave come across while working as part
OL,7,Fof this team, and I really want to
OL,8,Fcommend the bravery of the victim.
OL,10,F"Not only did the child report his
OL,11,Foffending, but they were present in
OL,12,Fcourt and personally read out their
OL,13,Fvictim impact statement, a step which
OL,14,Ftook great courage.
OL,16,F"I hope that the outcome of this case
OL,17,Fallows them to come to terms with
OL,18,Ftheir past and gives the closure
OL,19,Fneeded in order to move forward."
